nodes.text: A battle took place during the Clone Wars on the jungle planet Zeenada.
During the Clone Wars, the Confederacy of Independent Systems invaded Zeenada, establishing a base on the planet. The Republic deployed the 501st Legion, led by Anakin Skywalker and Ahsoka Tano.

Clone troopers Gunner and Sarge created a diversion behind enemy lines, while Skywalker and Tano led the main attack against the droid army. The Separatists were surprised and the Republic gained the upper hand. During the battle, Tano drew a swamp monster from the jungle to intercept the enemy. The battle ended in a Republic victory.
